Havas says uninterested in Ciby 2000 . French communications company Havas is not interested in buying film production company Ciby 2000 , a unit of construction giant Bouygues , a Havas spokesman said on Thursday . Havas has " studied and has no interest " in Ciby 2000 , the spokesman told Reuters . French media have reported that Bouygues was trying to sell Ciby , which has produced The Piano , Underground and Secrets and Lies . The U . S . entertainment newspaper Daily Variety has mentioned News Corp as another possible suitor . - - Paris newsroom + 33 1 4221 5452 
